Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Phantom\NPicture Drama"\N{\i1}Requiem for the Phantom, Picture Drama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"射击训练"\N{\i1}Requiem for the Phantom, Picture Drama.{\i0}
